<p><a href="/wiki/Second_Lieutenant" title="Second Lieutenant">Second Lieutenant</a> <b>Hiroo Onoda</b> (小野田 寛郎 <i>Onoda Hirō</i>; born <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1922-03-19"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="03-19"><a href="/wiki/March_19" title="March 19">March 19</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1922" title="1922">1922</a></span>) is a former <a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan">Japanese</a> army intelligence officer who fought in <a href="/wiki/World_War_II" title="World War II">World War II</a>, and did not surrender until 1974.</p>
